---
---

<article class="relative">
  <div class="space-y-12">

    <!-- Main About Section: Two Columns Layout -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-stretch">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Photo + Key Data -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
        <!-- Profile Photo -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative w-full aspect-square">
            <!-- Animated glow -->
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/20 via-purple-500/20 to-emerald-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-2xl animate-pulse"></div>
            
            <!-- Image container -->
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-50 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-1 shadow-2xl">
              <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                <img
                  src="/juli.jpeg"
                  alt="Julian Rojas"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Key Information Card -->
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-[1px] bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/40 to-emerald-500/40">
          <div class="relative bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase font-semibold tracking-widest mb-1">Nombre</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Julian Rojas</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-3 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase font-semibold tracking-widest mb-1">Rol</p>
              <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold">Software Engineer & Full Stack Developer</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-3 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase font-semibold tracking-widest mb-2">Contacto</p>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <a href="mailto:julis0293@gmail.com" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">
                  <span>📧</span> julis0293@gmail.com
                </a>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/julianrojasgonzalez" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">
                  <span>💼</span> LinkedIn
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Soft Skills Badges -->
            <div class="pt-3 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase font-semibold tracking-widest mb-3">Caracterización</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-100 to-teal-100 dark:from-emerald-900/30 dark:to-teal-900/30 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 text-xs font-semibold border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-700/50">🎯 Orientado a soluciones</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-cyan-100 dark:from-blue-900/30 dark:to-cyan-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 text-xs font-semibold border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700/50">💡 Autodidacta</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-pink-100 dark:from-purple-900/30 dark:to-pink-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-700/50">🤝 Trabajo en equipo</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-100 to-amber-100 dark:from-orange-900/30 dark:to-amber-900/30 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-400 text-xs font-semibold border border-orange-200 dark:border-orange-700/50">⚡ Resolutivo</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Vertical Divider -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex lg:col-span-1 justify-center">
        <div class="w-px h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-slate-300 dark:via-slate-600 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column: Narrative + Technologies -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-8">
        <!-- Main Narrative -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600">
              Mi Historia
            </span>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
            Ingeniero de sistemas apasionado por construir soluciones que funcionan sin excusas. Mi viaje tecnológico combina <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">infraestructura robusta, seguridad integrada y desarrollo full stack</span> — todo bajo una visión de arquitectura completa.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
            Especializado en transformar ideas complejas en experiencias digitales eficientes. Ya sea diseñando infraestructura segura para +500 usuarios, optimizando plataformas de alto volumen de datos, o liderando equipos técnicos — siempre busco <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">precisión, escalabilidad y excelencia</span>.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Technologies Grid -->
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Stack Tecnológico</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700/40 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <span class="text-2xl mb-1">⚙️</span>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 text-center">Backend</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-700/40 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <span class="text-2xl mb-1">🎨</span>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 text-center">Frontend</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/20 border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-700/40 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <span class="text-2xl mb-1">🔐</span>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 text-center">DevSecOps</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">¿Listo para explorar mi trabajo?</p>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <a href="#proyectos" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-emerald-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-sm">
              Ver Proyectos →
            </a>
            <a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border-2 border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900 transition-all duration-300 text-sm">
              Contactarme
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Three Core Competencies - Modern Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 py-8">
      <!-- Infraestructura Card -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-[1px] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/40 to-cyan-500/40">
        <div class="relative bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-8 h-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-white/20 dark:border-slate-800/50">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-cyan-100 dark:from-blue-900/30 dark:to-cyan-900/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
              <span class="text-3xl">⚙️</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Infraestructura</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Arquitectura segura, escalable y resiliente. DevSecOps, automatización e inteligencia de sistemas en producción.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Cloud · Backup · Monitoreo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Seguridad Card -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-[1px] bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/40 to-teal-500/40">
        <div class="relative bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-8 h-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-white/20 dark:border-slate-800/50">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-100 to-teal-100 dark:from-emerald-900/30 dark:to-teal-900/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
              <span class="text-3xl">🔐</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Seguridad</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Protección de activos digitales, auditoría de incidentes, integridad de datos y cumplimiento de SLAs.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Hacking · Ciberseguridad · CTF</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Desarrollo Card -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-[1px] bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/40 to-pink-500/40">
        <div class="relative bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-8 h-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-white/20 dark:border-slate-800/50">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-pink-100 dark:from-purple-900/30 dark:to-pink-900/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
              <span class="text-3xl">💻</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Desarrollo</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Full Stack con énfasis en rendimiento, experiencia del usuario y resiliencia. Backend → Frontend optimizado.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Web · Debugging · UX</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vintago Showcase - Premium Section -->
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl p-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600/60 via-pink-500/60 to-purple-600/60">
      <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-950 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl p-12 shadow-2xl border border-white/30 dark:border-slate-800/30">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-bl from-purple-400/10 via-pink-400/10 to-transparent rounded-full pointer-events-none blur-3xl"></div>
        
        <div class="relative space-y-6 max-w-3xl">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-pink-100 dark:from-purple-900/40 dark:to-pink-900/40 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-700/50">
              Laboratorio Creativo
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
              Vintago:
              <span class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 dark:from-purple-400 dark:to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Mi Mano Izquierda
              </span>
            </h3>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">
            Vintago es donde fusiono capacidad técnica con visión de producto y estética. Una marca de ropa que experimenta con branding, estrategia digital y desarrollo web como un ecosistema integrado. Es donde el ingeniero se convierte en emprendedor, probando hipótesis de negocio con rigor técnico.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 pt-4">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-purple-100 dark:from-purple-900/40 dark:to-purple-900/40 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 text-sm font-semibold border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-700/40">
              🎨 Branding
            </span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-100 to-pink-100 dark:from-pink-900/40 dark:to-pink-900/40 text-pink-700 dark:text-pink-300 text-sm font-semibold border border-pink-200 dark:border-pink-700/40">
              🛍️ E-commerce
            </span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-100 to-indigo-100 dark:from-indigo-900/40 dark:to-indigo-900/40 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300 text-sm font-semibold border border-indigo-200 dark:border-indigo-700/40">
              💡 Emprendimiento
            </span>
            <a href="https://vintago.com.co/" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to-slate-800 dark:from-slate-100 dark:to-slate-200 text-white dark:text-slate-900 text-sm font-semibold hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              Visitar →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</article>
